---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Custom Dentures in Footscray | Comfortable, Natural-Looking Solutions"
  description="Regain your smile and confidence with custom dentures from Top Dentists Footscray. Our comfortable, natural-looking dentures are tailored to fit your needs, restoring both function and aesthetics to your smile."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-background">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <nav class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-6">
          <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2">
            <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Home</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li><a href="/services" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Services</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li class="text-neutral-800 font-medium">Dentures</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h1 class="text-h1 font-heading font-bold text-neutral-800">
            Custom Dentures
          </h1>
          
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              Missing teeth can affect your ability to eat, speak, and smile confidently. At Top Dentists Footscray, we offer high-quality dentures to restore your smile and oral function.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              Our dentists take precise impressions and measurements to create dentures that fit comfortably and look natural. Benefits of dentures include improved appearance, better chewing and speech abilities, and a confidence boost.
            </p>

            <!-- Denture Types -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg space-y-6 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-6">
                Our Denture Options
              </h3>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Complete Dentures</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Recommended when all natural teeth are missing. These dentures replace a full arch of upper and/or lower teeth, providing complete restoration of your smile and function.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Partial Dentures</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Used when some natural teeth remain. These dentures fill in the gaps left by missing teeth and are secured by clasps or precision attachments to your remaining teeth.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Implant-Supported Dentures</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Dentures that are anchored to dental implants for superior stability and a secure fit. These provide increased comfort and confidence when eating and speaking.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Benefits of Dentures -->
            <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-xl p-8 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4">
                Benefits of Custom Dentures
              </h3>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Improved Appearance</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Restore your facial structure and youthful smile</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Better Function</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Enhanced chewing and speech abilities</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Increased Confidence</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Smile, laugh, and socialize without worry</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Affordable Solution</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Cost-effective way to replace multiple teeth</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Denture Process -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg space-y-6 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-6">
                The Denture Creation Process
              </h3>

              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div class="space-y-4">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800">Initial Appointments:</h4>
                  <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
                    <li>• Comprehensive oral examination</li>
                    <li>• Precise impressions of your mouth</li>
                    <li>• Measurements for proper fit</li>
                    <li>• Color and shape selection</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800">Fitting Process:</h4>
                  <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
                    <li>• Try-in appointments for adjustments</li>
                    <li>• Fine-tuning for comfort</li>
                    <li>• Final delivery and instructions</li>
                    <li>• Follow-up care and adjustments</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Adjustment Period -->
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 rounded-xl p-8 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4">
                Adjusting to Your New Dentures
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                There is typically an adjustment period when you first receive dentures. This is completely normal as your mouth adapts to the new appliance.
              </p>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                <div class="text-center">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-yellow-700 text-sm mb-1">Week 1-2</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-xs">Initial adaptation, soft foods recommended</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-yellow-700 text-sm mb-1">Week 3-4</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-xs">Increased comfort, gradual diet expansion</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-yellow-700 text-sm mb-1">Month 2+</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-xs">Full adaptation, normal eating and speaking</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Denture Care -->
            <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-8 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4">
                Caring for Your Dentures
              </h3>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-700 mb-2">Daily Maintenance:</h4>
                  <ul class="space-y-1 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
                    <li>• Clean dentures daily with special brush</li>
                    <li>• Remove and rinse after eating</li>
                    <li>• Soak overnight in denture cleanser</li>
                    <li>• Handle carefully to avoid damage</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-700 mb-2">Regular Care:</h4>
                  <ul class="space-y-1 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
                    <li>• Professional cleanings and check-ups</li>
                    <li>• Adjustments as needed</li>
                    <li>• Monitor fit and comfort</li>
                    <li>• Replace when worn or damaged</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Types Comparison -->
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  Denture Solutions for Every Need
                </h3>
                <div class="space-y-3">
                  <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 text-sm">Conventional Dentures</h4>
                    <p class="text-neutral-600 text-xs">Traditional removable option, most affordable</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 text-sm">Immediate Dentures</h4>
                    <p class="text-neutral-600 text-xs">Placed right after extractions, no waiting period</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 text-sm">Implant-Retained</h4>
                    <p class="text-neutral-600 text-xs">Secured by implants, superior stability</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  Expected Lifespan
                </h3>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                  <p class="text-primary-600 font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
                    5-10 years
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">
                    With proper care and regular adjustments, dentures provide reliable function. Periodic relines or replacements may be needed as your mouth changes.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary-500 text-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 observe-fade">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-h2 font-heading font-semibold">
          Ready to Restore Your Smile with Dentures?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-100">
          Don't let missing teeth diminish your quality of life. Call
          <a
            href="tel:96875050"
            class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-primary-100 transition-colors"
          >
            9687 5050
          </a>
          for custom dentures tailored to your needs
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://apac.dentalhub.online/soe/new/%20?pid=AUTOP01"
          class="btn bg-white text-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-50 text-lg inline-block"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Book now
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>